com.analog.lyric.dimple.model.domains

Class FiniteFieldNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • com.analog.lyric.dimple.model.domains.FiniteFieldNumber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Immutable
public class FiniteFieldNumber
extends java.lang.Number
    An extension of Number that includes additional information needed to fully define arithmetic operations on a finite field of characteristic 2 (GF(2^N)). This includes a binary representation of the primitive polynomial and the length in bits.
